&lt;li&gt;Relevant professional certifications such as Certified Information Systems Security Professional, Certified Information Security Manager, Certified in Risk and Information Systems Control, CompTIA Cybersecurity Analyst or Certified Fraud Examiner&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Exposure to AI governance, model risk, or responsible-AI program work&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Knowledge of privacy legislation and regulations such as HIPAA and GDPR&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience working with security and risk tooling in cloud infrastructure, hosting, and platform contexts&lt;/li&gt;
